title: Start
---

-> Option 1 <<once if $conditionB>> #line:015ad44 // only selectable once, and only if $conditionB is true
-> Option 2 <<once>> #line:015ad45 // only selectable once
-> Option 3 <<if $conditionB>> #line:015ad46 // only selectable if $conditionB is true
-> Option 4 #line:015ad47 // always selectable

=> Item 1 <<once>> #line:015ad48 // will only appear once
=> Item 2 <<once if $conditionC>> #line:015ad49 // will only appear once, and only if $conditionC is true
=> Item 3 <<if $conditionC>> #line:015ad50 // will only appear if $conditionC is true
=> Item 4 #line:015ad51 // may always appear

Line 1 <<once>> #line:015ad52 // line will only run once
Line 2 <<once if $conditionD>> #line:015ad53 // line will only run once, and only if $conditionD is true
Line 3 <<if $conditionD>> #line:015ad54 // line will only run if $conditionD is true
Line 4 #line:015ad55 // line will always run
===